00057 static void rna_Image_animated_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *UNUSED(scene), PointerRNA *ptr)
00058 {
00059     Image *ima = (Image*)ptr->data;
00060     int  nr;
00061 
00062     if (ima->flag & IMA_TWINANIM) {
00063         nr = ima->xrep*ima->yrep;
00064         if (ima->twsta >= nr) ima->twsta = 1;
00065         if (ima->twend >= nr) ima->twend = nr-1;
00066         if (ima->twsta>ima->twend) ima->twsta = 1;
00067     }
00068 }

00089 static void rna_Image_fields_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *UNUSED(scene), PointerRNA *ptr)
00090 {
00091     Image *ima = ptr->id.data;
00092     ImBuf *ibuf;
00093     void *lock;
00094 
00095     ibuf = BKE_image_acquire_ibuf(ima, NULL, &lock);
00096 
00097     if (ibuf) {
00098         short nr = 0;
00099 
00100         if (!(ima->flag & IMA_FIELDS) && (ibuf->flags & IB_fields)) nr = 1;
00101         if ((ima->flag & IMA_FIELDS) && !(ibuf->flags & IB_fields)) nr = 1;
00102 
00103         if (nr)
00104             BKE_image_signal(ima, NULL, IMA_SIGNAL_FREE);
00105     }
00106 
00107     BKE_image_release_ibuf(ima, lock);
00108 }

00155 static EnumPropertyItem *rna_Image_source_itemf(bContext *UNUSED(C), PointerRNA *ptr,
00156                                                 PropertyRNA *UNUSED(prop), int *free)
00157 {
00158     Image *ima = (Image*)ptr->data;
00159     EnumPropertyItem *item = NULL;
00160     int totitem = 0;
00161     
00162     if (ima->source == IMA_SRC_VIEWER) {
00163         RNA_enum_items_add_value(&item, &totitem, image_source_items, IMA_SRC_VIEWER);
00164     }
00165     else {
00166         RNA_enum_items_add_value(&item, &totitem, image_source_items, IMA_SRC_FILE);
00167         RNA_enum_items_add_value(&item, &totitem, image_source_items, IMA_SRC_SEQUENCE);
00168         RNA_enum_items_add_value(&item, &totitem, image_source_items, IMA_SRC_MOVIE);
00169         RNA_enum_items_add_value(&item, &totitem, image_source_items, IMA_SRC_GENERATED);
00170     }
00171 
00172     RNA_enum_item_end(&item, &totitem);
00173     *free = 1;
00174 
00175     return item;
00176 }

00268 static int rna_Image_depth_get(PointerRNA *ptr)
00269 {
00270     Image *im = (Image*)ptr->data;
00271     ImBuf *ibuf;
00272     void *lock;
00273     int planes;
00274     
00275     ibuf = BKE_image_acquire_ibuf(im, NULL, &lock);
00276 
00277     if (!ibuf)
00278         planes = 0;
00279     else if (ibuf->rect_float)
00280         planes = ibuf->planes * 4;
00281     else
00282         planes = ibuf->planes;
00283 
00284     BKE_image_release_ibuf(im, lock);
00285 
00286     return planes;

00307 static void rna_Image_pixels_get(PointerRNA *ptr, float *values)
00308 {
00309     Image *ima = ptr->id.data;
00310     ImBuf *ibuf;
00311     void *lock;
00312     int i, size;
00313 
00314     ibuf = BKE_image_acquire_ibuf(ima, NULL, &lock);
00315 
00316     if (ibuf) {
00317         size = ibuf->x*ibuf->y*ibuf->channels;
00318 
00319         if (ibuf->rect_float) {
00320             memcpy(values, ibuf->rect_float, sizeof(float)*size);
00321         }
00322         else {
00323             for (i = 0; i < size; i++)
00324                 values[i] = ((unsigned char*)ibuf->rect)[i]*(1.0f/255.0f);
00325         }
00326     }
00327 
00328     BKE_image_release_ibuf(ima, lock);
00329 }
